leadingComments.value: Logarithmic depth buffer involves an accuracy tradeoff, sacrificing
accuracy at close range to improve accuracy at long range. This can
mess up accuracy for occlusion tests, so we'll disable for now.
COLOR_OPAQUE // Only opaque objects can be occluders
